# livekit/ — LiveKit integration package
#
# Sub-packages:
#   //livekit/token    — JWT token generation (participant + admin)
#   //livekit/webhook  — Webhook HTTP server (uWebSockets)
#   //livekit/crypto   — E2EE key management per voice channel
#   //livekit/cli      — RoomService Twirp HTTP client
#   //livekit/routing  — Node registry and load balancing
